data.description: Picture perfect! This wonderful WHISPERING PINE Designer will surely impress with UPGRADES at every turn. Situated in a quiet cul-de-sac in the Village of Polo Ridge, just move in and start enjoying all the amenities available within just minutes by golf cart.  You’ll feel right at home as you enter this light, bright and happy home with VAULTED Ceilings, GORGEOUS Laminate Floors and 2 Solar Tubes in the main living area…and the BOND IS PAID!  Your eyes will carry to the  South-Facing GLASS ENCLOSED Lanai which offers air and heat for year-round comfort, making the effective living area 1700 square feet...and the Shades and Landscaping provide a bit of PRIVACY! The Spacious Kitchen has received a beautiful make-over with Quality QUARTZ COUNTERS, Painted Cabinets, Pot Drawers, Stainless Appliances with Gas Cooktop, Pull-out Shelves (even in the Pantry), Custom Backsplash, Custom Lighting and Accent Lighting.  The sunny breakfast nook is perfect for casual dining with a breakfast bar. The Master Suite has a Spacious CUSTOMIZED Walk-in Closet and the En-Suite Bath has QUARTZ Counters with Dual sinks, and a Tiled Shower. The Guest Bedroom is perfect for the occasional guest and the Guest Bath also boasts QUARTZ counters with a Tub/Shower combo.  The 3rd Bedroom/Den has a full wall BUILT-IN around the window – very nice! The 2-car garage is extra deep, includes attic stairs, ceiling fan, plus an additional refrigerator which will convey. The garage door opener was replaced just a couple of years ago. Many extras include Paver drive, window treatments, gutters, keyless entry and much more!  Maintenance items:  ROOF and A/C replaced in 2017, and Water Heater in 2016. BOND IS PAID! This home has been beautifully maintained by the original owners.  So, what are you waiting for? If not now, when???
